          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1601376191917-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 15 min or until the veg has softened and the fish is cooked through – this is your <strong>fiery coconut basa and vegetables</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1601376197336-x200.jpg",
